@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_txtwvv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    tmp = (0.66 * v0)
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.32) - 0.83))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v2 + 0.34 + tmp + 0.29)))
    v2 = 0.84
    data[tid] = v0
